  <text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink223-kilavi">  varaiviṭai vaittup pirinta talaimakaṉ kuṟitta paruvattiṟku muṉṉē varukiṉṟamai aṟinta tōḻi talaimakaṭku makiḻntu colliyatu. </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">What the confidante happily told the heroine; [the confidante] who knew that the hero, [though] having placed an interval [before the time of] marriage and separated, had come [back] earlier than the appointed season.</p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink223">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi nammalai</l>
<l>varaiyā miḻiyak kōṭa ṉīṭak</l>
<l>kātalarp pirintōr kaiyaṟa naliyun</l>
<l>taṇpaṉi vaṭantai yaccira</l>
<l>muntuvan taṉarnaṅ kāta lōrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>  O friend! </l>
        <l rend="indent">Our lover came before the cold season </l>
        <l rend="indent2">with its cool dew and northern winds,  </l>
        <l rend="indent3">which afflicts so separated lovers are helpless, </l>
        <l rend="indent3"> as the hilly waters of our mountain tumble down, </l>
        <l rend="indent3"> and as the white Malabar Glory lilies [grow] long. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
